the governments of Brazil and Bolivia have attached to the 
natural gas purchase contract signed by Petrobras [Brazilian 
Petroleum Corporation] and Bolivian Government Oil Deposits. 
  [Begin Amorim recording] At this meeting I obviously could 
not discuss technical details because this must be done by the 
Petrobras people. But I believe the important thing is the 
political reaffirmation of our determination to develop this 
project, which is important for Bolivia and also very important 
for Brazil. [end recording] 
